# Public toolkit repo: track the generic skills, commands, workflow, docs, and
# scripts. Keep OS cruft, runtime output, and any personal/proprietary overlays
# out of version control.

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~

# Dependencies (e.g. learning projects under artifacts/)
node_modules/

# Tool-managed lock/manifest + local scratch
.skill-lock.json
*.out

# Personal / proprietary overlays — never commit (keep these local-only)
*.local.md
docs/profile.local.md
**/project-profile.md

# Runtime working data (per-feature workflow state, saved reports)
artifacts/

# Personal work-activity outputs and generators (keep private)
wiki/
